# The fourth letter of the [[Arabic]] alphabet. Its name is {{ARchar|[[Ш«Ш§ШЎ]]}} (ОёДҒвҖҷ) and it has the sound of '''[[Оё]]''' in English '''<u>th</u>'''ing. It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[ШӘ]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[Ш¬]]}}.
# The twenty-third letter in traditional [[abjad]] order, which is used in place of numerals for list numbering ([[abjad numerals]]). It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[ШӘ]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[Ш®]]}}.

